==English==

===Noun===
'''continent''' (''plural:'' [[continents]])

#A large contiguous landmass that is at least partially surrounded by water. Americans consider that the [[Earth]] has seven:
*[[Africa]]
*[[Antarctica]]
*[[Asia]]
*[[Europe]]
*[[North America]]
*[[Oceania]] ([[Australia]] and [[New Zealand]])
*[[South America]]

Most Europeans and Latin Americans count only five continents:
*[[Africa]]
*[[America]]
*[[Asia]]
*[[Europe]]
*[[Oceania]]

